tamente, en ti y dejaremos que los Hijos de Israel partan contigo\u00bb.","french":"134. Et quand le ch\u00e2timent les frappa, ils dirent : \"\u00f4 Mo\u00efse, invoque pour nous ton Seigneur en vertu de l'engagement qu'Il t'a donn\u00e9. Si tu \u00e9loignes de nous le ch\u00e2timent, nous croirons certes en toi et laisserons partir avec toi les enfants d'Isra\u00ebl\".","spell":"Walammaa waqa'a 'alaihimurrijzu qaaluuu yaa muusaad'u lanaa rabbaka bimaa 'ahida 'indaka la-in kasyafta 'annaarrijza lanu'minanna laka walanursilanna ma'aka banii israa-iil(a)"},{"arabic":"\u0661\u0663\u0665.  \t\u0641\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0645\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0643\u064e\u0634\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f\u0645\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u0650\u062c\u0652\u0632\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0649\u0670 \u0623\u064e\u062c\u064e\u0644\u064d \u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0628\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u063a\u064f\u0648\u0647\u064f \u0625\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0643\u064f\u062b\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e","english":"135.  \tBut when We removed the punishment from them to a fixed term, which they had to reach, behold! they broke their word!","indonesian":"135. Maka setelah Kami hilangkan azab itu dari mereka hingga batas waktu yang mereka sampai kepadanya, tiba-tiba mereka mengingkarinya.","japanese":"135. &#12384;&#12364;&#65292;&#23450;&#12417;&#12425;&#12428;&#12383;&#26399;&#38480;&#12395;&#12394;&#12387;&#12390;&#65292;&#12431;&#12428;&#12364;&#12363;&#12428;&#12425;&#12363;&#12425;&#28797;&#21380;&#12434;&#38500;&#12367;&#24230;&#12395;&#65292;&#35211;&#12394;&#12373;&#12356;&#12290;&#12363;&#12428;&#12425;&#12399;&#65288;&#12381;&#12398;&#32004;&#26463;&#12434;&#65289;&#30772;&#12429;&#12290;","korean":"135. \uadf8\ub9ac\ud558\uc5ec \ud558\ub098\ub2d8\uc774 \uadf8\ub4e4\uc5d0 \uac8c\uc11c \uadf8 \uc5ed\ubcd1\uc744 \uac70\ub450\uc5b4 \uc8fc\ub2c8 \uc77c\uc815 \ud55c \uae30\uac04 \ubfd0\uc774\ub7